Class NetworkMemoryReport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.nn.conf.memory.MemoryReport
      • org.deeplearning4j.nn.conf.memory.NetworkMemoryReport

  • public class NetworkMemoryReport
extends MemoryReport
    Network memory reports is a class that is used to store/represent the memory requirements of a MultiLayerNetwork or ComputationGraph, composed of multiple layers and/or vertices.
